            <if test="JSDOC.opt.D.copyright">&copy;{+JSDOC.opt.D.copyright+}<br /></if>
            Documentation generated by <a href="http://code.google.com/p/jsdoc-toolkit/" target="_blank">JsDoc Toolkit</a> {+JSDOC.VERSION+} on {+new Date()+}
        </div>

    </div>
